Package com.ecom.exceptions

package com.ecom.exceptions
Provides custom exception classes to handle the exception effectively

This package contains custom exceptions to handle the exception effectively

Example usages include:

  • FrameworkExceptions acts as parent custom exception which extends RuntimeException class to provide custom exceptions specific to the framework
  • InValidBrowserEnteredException
  • InValidExcelPathException
  • InValidPropertyKeyException
  • InValidSparkConfigPathException
  • InValidWaitStrategyException
  • InValidBrowserEnteredException
  • UnableToLoadFileInBrowserException
  • Exception Classes
    Class
    Description
    FrameworkExceptions
    Custom runtime exception class for framework-specific exceptions.
    InValidBrowserEnteredException
    Exception thrown when an invalid browser name is provided.
    InValidExcelPathException
    Exception thrown when an invalid Excel file path is provided.
    InValidPropertyKeyException
    Exception thrown when an invalid property key is provided.
    InValidSparkConfigPathException
    Exception thrown when an invalid Spark configuration path is provided.
    InValidWaitStrategyException
    Exception thrown when an invalid wait strategy is provided.
    UnableToLoadFileInBrowserException
    Exception thrown when unable to load a file in the browser.
